WEBVTT

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:08.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:00:09.260 --> 00:00:12.130
Hold your soul and body as one.

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:14.000
First, observe Heaven‌.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:15.630
[Wu Gen]

00:00:15.630 --> 00:00:17.970
[Xiaobangchui] ‌Second, observe Earth‌.

00:00:19.020 --> 00:00:21.360
‌Third, observe people‌.

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:24.160
The artwork is so bad.

00:00:24.540 --> 00:00:25.730
And they charged me 30 wen?

00:00:25.940 --> 00:00:26.580
Save me!

00:00:26.750 --> 00:00:27.360
Darn it.

00:00:27.630 --> 00:00:28.410
Master, slow down.

00:00:28.430 --> 00:00:29.640
- Master! - Master!

00:00:29.860 --> 00:00:30.730
Stay back!

00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:35.570
The demon hiding in your estate is powerful

00:00:35.950 --> 00:00:40.290
And very cunning. It's quite troublesome.

00:00:42.230 --> 00:00:46.120
Xiaobangchui, have you found out what kind of demon it is?

00:00:49.060 --> 00:00:50.250
I've figured it out, Master.

00:00:51.660 --> 00:00:52.570
This trip is dangerous.

00:00:54.380 --> 00:00:56.810
This demon is called Tanmei. It feeds on human life force.

00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:58.320
At best, it brings illness and misfortune.

00:00:58.550 --> 00:01:01.040
At worst, you'll see blood within ten days.

00:01:01.060 --> 00:01:02.320
Master, it's a bad omen!

00:01:03.310 --> 00:01:06.810
Master, please save my family!

00:01:06.830 --> 00:01:08.370
Please save me.

00:01:08.390 --> 00:01:10.250
Sir, please rise.

00:01:11.110 --> 00:01:13.320
I'll do my best.

00:01:14.220 --> 00:01:15.370
Master, no!

00:01:15.940 --> 00:01:17.970
Defeating this great demon will cost you 30 years of your life.

00:01:17.990 --> 00:01:18.920
It'll damage your very core.

00:01:18.940 --> 00:01:21.120
Only a thousand-year Ganoderma lucidum can restore it, Master.

00:01:21.140 --> 00:01:21.680
Well...

00:01:23.060 --> 00:01:25.810
Master, here's the money for the Ganoderma lucidum.

00:01:28.670 --> 00:01:29.650
Everyone, watch out!

00:01:34.860 --> 00:01:38.650
Heaven and earth, source of all energy.

00:01:38.830 --> 00:01:41.810
By this talisman, reveal yourself, demon!

00:01:41.830 --> 00:01:42.730
Go!

00:01:49.700 --> 00:01:51.730
Demon! There it is!

00:01:52.910 --> 00:01:54.530
A demon! Look, right there!

00:01:54.550 --> 00:01:55.200
Right there!

00:01:57.830 --> 00:01:59.970
Take the money to solve their problem. Be quick.

00:02:00.140 --> 00:02:01.320
Me again?

00:02:02.140 --> 00:02:03.370
Who else, me?

00:02:06.990 --> 00:02:08.050
Master, hold the fort here.

00:02:08.230 --> 00:02:09.280
I'll go handle the demon.

00:02:12.620 --> 00:02:13.970
- Such skill! - Indeed.

00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:31.520
[Ancestral Hall]

00:02:33.620 --> 00:02:34.970
By the power of the spirits, break!

00:02:59.600 --> 00:03:01.080
[Lei Xiuyuan]

00:03:23.180 --> 00:03:23.930
Who are you?

00:03:23.950 --> 00:03:24.930
- You're not from Longming Sanctuary. - You are...?

00:03:29.140 --> 00:03:29.720
No, wait.

00:03:30.670 --> 00:03:31.770
Whether you're human or a demon,

00:03:32.110 --> 00:03:33.090
Can we talk this out?

00:03:33.670 --> 00:03:35.650
Just find another place to stay.

00:03:35.670 --> 00:03:37.280
Stop bothering the owners of this house.

00:03:44.830 --> 00:03:45.840
What a fierce demon.

00:03:47.620 --> 00:03:49.120
Bind the soul and expel evil, seal!

00:04:00.950 --> 00:04:03.330
Sir, the demon you're looking for is right here.

00:04:03.580 --> 00:04:06.370
I... I'm just passing by.

00:04:06.550 --> 00:04:07.330
You menace!

00:04:07.830 --> 00:04:08.930
You're the menace here!

00:04:24.420 --> 00:04:25.160
Go die somewhere else!

00:04:28.260 --> 00:04:29.400
What's wrong with you?

00:05:16.590 --> 00:05:19.600
Master, I'll see you in the next life!

00:05:38.910 --> 00:05:42.210
Senior Brother, you finally showed up.

00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:39.580
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:06:39.580 --> 00:06:43.880
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:06:43.880 --> 00:06:46.880
[Episode 1]

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:50.120
[Qingqiu]

00:07:01.380 --> 00:07:02.010
Go away.

00:07:04.670 --> 00:07:05.280
Master!

00:07:06.380 --> 00:07:07.770
Master! Master?

00:07:08.820 --> 00:07:09.600
Master!

00:07:19.710 --> 00:07:20.690
You old geezer!

00:07:20.820 --> 00:07:22.280
You always bail whenever there's trouble.

00:07:22.380 --> 00:07:23.570
What kind of master does that?

00:07:24.620 --> 00:07:27.600
You are so clever.

00:07:27.790 --> 00:07:30.450
You'll always find a way out of trouble.

00:07:31.790 --> 00:07:32.360
Oh,

00:07:34.030 --> 00:07:34.770
I got this for you.

00:07:35.990 --> 00:07:37.040
You're wasting money again!

00:07:37.470 --> 00:07:39.210
Is it easy for us to make money

00:07:39.230 --> 00:07:40.600
By pulling these scams?

00:07:40.620 --> 00:07:41.770
And you keep buying stuff!

00:07:42.500 --> 00:07:43.920
Open it up.

00:07:47.110 --> 00:07:48.010
Do you like it?

00:07:49.820 --> 00:07:51.600
Are you still

00:07:51.670 --> 00:07:52.650
My stingy master

00:07:52.790 --> 00:07:54.600
Who wouldn't even buy me candy?

00:07:55.940 --> 00:07:56.970
What are you talking about?

00:07:57.300 --> 00:07:58.770
If you like it, wear it.

00:07:58.790 --> 00:08:00.800
If not, I'll return it!

00:08:06.910 --> 00:08:07.600
Xiaobangchui!

00:08:09.110 --> 00:08:10.650
You're a girl. Don't you know

00:08:10.670 --> 00:08:12.650
You're supposed to change in your own room?

00:08:14.110 --> 00:08:16.480
Of course, it's not all your fault.

00:08:16.710 --> 00:08:17.650
I'm to blame too.

00:08:17.820 --> 00:08:20.090
I've always treated you like your senior brother.

00:08:20.300 --> 00:08:22.400
I've practically raised you like a boy.

00:08:24.620 --> 00:08:26.240
You keep talking about him.

00:08:26.790 --> 00:08:27.530
But I've never seen him

00:08:27.550 --> 00:08:29.090
Since I can remember.

00:08:30.060 --> 00:08:31.480
Did you just make him up?

00:08:32.020 --> 00:08:34.120
Have I ever lied to you?

00:08:34.190 --> 00:08:35.450
Your senior brother

00:08:35.900 --> 00:08:38.570
Is smarter than you. Extremely talented.

00:08:38.950 --> 00:08:40.240
By the time he was in his teens,

00:08:40.260 --> 00:08:42.120
I had nothing left to teach him.

00:08:42.140 --> 00:08:42.840
Eventually,

00:08:42.990 --> 00:08:45.240
He got into Chufeng Academy on his own.

00:08:45.990 --> 00:08:47.600
Then keep thinking about him.

00:08:48.830 --> 00:08:50.520
I'm going to change into my new clothes.

00:08:50.540 --> 00:08:52.290
Fine. Then get the radish stew going.

00:08:52.310 --> 00:08:53.290
I'm hungry.

00:08:54.500 --> 00:08:57.050
You had money but didn't buy meat?

00:08:57.070 --> 00:08:58.120
You're so cheap!

00:08:58.740 --> 00:09:00.410
Add more salt. I like it salty.

00:09:00.430 --> 00:09:01.840
Got it.

00:09:02.540 --> 00:09:03.290
Xiaobangchui.

00:09:04.260 --> 00:09:06.120
What now?

00:09:12.900 --> 00:09:15.720
Nothing. Just be careful when you cook.

00:09:16.470 --> 00:09:17.570
Don't get your new clothes dirty.

00:09:17.830 --> 00:09:19.290
I'm not as unreliable as you.

00:09:33.620 --> 00:09:38.000
Xiuyuan, put me down. Just leave me behind.

00:09:38.950 --> 00:09:39.930
Don't talk nonsense.

00:09:40.500 --> 00:09:41.600
[Lu Shanhua] We said

00:09:41.950 --> 00:09:43.120
We'd find a place where no one knows us.

00:09:43.430 --> 00:09:44.690
We can farm or fish.

00:09:45.140 --> 00:09:46.520
Just never live a life on the run again.

00:09:47.740 --> 00:09:48.570
You can't leave me.

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:02.880
[Young Lei Xiuyuan]

00:10:23.310 --> 00:10:24.690
My spirit meridians are completely broken.

00:10:25.540 --> 00:10:26.810
I don't have much time left.

00:10:27.830 --> 00:10:29.050
I can't drag you down.

00:10:30.590 --> 00:10:32.290
Isn't that what family do? Drag each other down?

00:10:33.500 --> 00:10:34.480
When Gaolu fell,

00:10:35.190 --> 00:10:36.090
Our whole family

00:10:36.430 --> 00:10:38.090
Went down together.

00:10:39.310 --> 00:10:41.210
We made it out and survived this long

00:10:41.620 --> 00:10:43.210
Because heaven wants us to live.

00:10:48.590 --> 00:10:50.090
Soup's ready!

00:10:52.620 --> 00:10:54.120
Why are you using an evasion spell at home?

00:10:54.140 --> 00:10:55.050
Are you hiding money or something?

00:10:58.310 --> 00:10:58.930
Master?

00:11:00.230 --> 00:11:00.930
Master?

00:11:04.500 --> 00:11:05.600
Where's Master?

00:11:06.380 --> 00:11:07.050
Master?

00:11:10.740 --> 00:11:11.480
Master!

00:11:12.500 --> 00:11:13.520
Master!

00:11:26.310 --> 00:11:27.170
Xiaobangchui,

00:11:27.470 --> 00:11:29.330
I must leave for something urgent.

00:11:29.500 --> 00:11:30.480
Can't take you with me.

00:11:31.260 --> 00:11:33.450
Go to Chufeng Academy to find your senior brother.

00:11:33.860 --> 00:11:35.840
I've included his portrait with the letter.

00:11:36.110 --> 00:11:37.690
He seems quite capable.

00:11:37.710 --> 00:11:38.760
You can't go wrong with him.

00:11:46.380 --> 00:11:48.170
Why suddenly ask me to find some senior brother?

00:11:49.950 --> 00:11:51.000
You didn't even take your bag?

00:12:00.070 --> 00:12:01.520
He left all the money to me?

00:12:04.350 --> 00:12:05.090
Master.

00:12:13.540 --> 00:12:14.290
Master!

00:12:15.990 --> 00:12:17.000
Master!

00:12:20.830 --> 00:12:22.170
Master!

00:12:39.350 --> 00:12:40.170
You old geezer!

00:12:41.740 --> 00:12:43.000
You abandoned me.

00:12:43.620 --> 00:12:45.330
I can't live on my own!

00:12:48.230 --> 00:12:49.410
I might as well die!

00:12:58.430 --> 00:13:02.290
Help, Master! I'm dying!

00:13:06.500 --> 00:13:08.000
That heartless old geezer!

00:13:22.950 --> 00:13:23.570
Silly me.

00:13:24.110 --> 00:13:26.000
That old man always fears death. He won't come save me.

00:13:29.310 --> 00:13:30.000
That's not right.

00:13:31.310 --> 00:13:32.170
If he's scared of dying,

00:13:32.710 --> 00:13:34.570
He should hide with more money.

00:13:35.620 --> 00:13:36.360
Unless...

00:13:37.660 --> 00:13:39.720
Unless he ran into some life-threatening danger

00:13:40.020 --> 00:13:41.170
And knew he probably wouldn't make it?

00:13:41.190 --> 00:13:42.120
That's why he left me behind?

00:13:43.620 --> 00:13:45.720
Master... Master's in trouble.

00:14:04.350 --> 00:14:04.930
Demon.

00:14:05.280 --> 00:14:06.320
[Nine-Tailed Fox, Riyan]

00:14:07.110 --> 00:14:07.810
A fox spirit!

00:14:33.620 --> 00:14:34.450
You're hurt?

00:14:53.450 --> 00:14:54.880
[Immortal Dongyang, Wuyue Court]

00:15:05.470 --> 00:15:06.720
[Zhenyunzi, Xingzheng Hall] Why is there a mortal in Qingqiu?

00:15:08.730 --> 00:15:09.900
[Lady Longjing, Huolian Abbey]

00:15:09.900 --> 00:15:10.880
It's a child.

00:15:11.500 --> 00:15:12.450
Who are you?

00:15:13.350 --> 00:15:14.840
Why are you alone in this deep forest?

00:15:26.540 --> 00:15:27.520
Whose blood is this?

00:15:33.900 --> 00:15:34.810
Mine. I got hurt.

00:15:38.430 --> 00:15:40.330
Tell me, what did you see?

00:15:43.110 --> 00:15:45.290
So cold. He's casting a spell on me.

00:15:51.230 --> 00:15:51.930
Mr. Zhenyun,

00:15:52.500 --> 00:15:53.880
She's just an ordinary person.

00:15:54.350 --> 00:15:56.170
She can't handle your verbal command spell.

00:16:00.380 --> 00:16:01.120
Don't be scared.

00:16:01.860 --> 00:16:02.930
Where's your family?

00:16:03.780 --> 00:16:05.880
Why did you come into the mountains alone?

00:16:06.070 --> 00:16:08.970
I... I live up in the mountains with my master.

00:16:09.230 --> 00:16:10.410
But my master disappeared.

00:16:10.830 --> 00:16:11.930
I've been looking for him everywhere.

00:16:11.950 --> 00:16:14.480
I don't know... where he is.

00:16:16.500 --> 00:16:17.410
Who's your master?

00:16:19.070 --> 00:16:20.570
Wu... Wu Gen.

00:16:22.260 --> 00:16:23.360
Wu Gen?

00:16:28.380 --> 00:16:30.880
There are countless reclusive cultivators in this world.

00:16:33.190 --> 00:16:35.410
This girl has a pure aura.

00:16:36.350 --> 00:16:38.970
She must be a good person.

00:16:43.660 --> 00:16:45.720
Don't be afraid, child.

00:16:46.190 --> 00:16:49.050
Did you see a white-furred fox spirit

00:16:49.070 --> 00:16:50.090
Pass by just now?

00:16:57.070 --> 00:16:57.760
Where did it go?

00:16:58.230 --> 00:16:58.880
There!

00:16:59.310 --> 00:17:00.840
A white shadow

00:17:00.860 --> 00:17:01.840
Just flew that way.

00:17:30.540 --> 00:17:32.450
Tell me, where's the fox?

00:17:32.950 --> 00:17:34.080
I don't know what you're talking about!

00:17:34.100 --> 00:17:34.890
Let me go!

00:17:35.780 --> 00:17:36.800
What about Riyan?

00:17:37.390 --> 00:17:39.080
What Riyan? I don't know anything about that!

00:17:39.100 --> 00:17:41.480
I don't know who Riyan is!

00:17:41.950 --> 00:17:42.480
Speak!

00:17:43.950 --> 00:17:44.760
If you kill me,

00:17:45.150 --> 00:17:46.370
You'll never find out!

00:17:46.950 --> 00:17:47.690
Speak!

00:17:57.670 --> 00:17:59.760
This girl is looking for her family.

00:18:00.430 --> 00:18:03.040
Please spare her.

00:18:05.230 --> 00:18:06.080
Please, have mercy.

00:18:06.470 --> 00:18:07.320
Let me go.

00:18:25.740 --> 00:18:28.800
Sir, your vital energy was already unstable.

00:18:29.260 --> 00:18:31.080
And now you've been badly wounded by the fox.

00:18:31.670 --> 00:18:33.450
If you don't retreat to heal soon,

00:18:33.780 --> 00:18:36.800
You might go berserk.

00:18:40.340 --> 00:18:45.080
Thanks for the warning. I'll spar with you another day.

00:18:58.540 --> 00:18:59.320
Mr. Dongyang,

00:19:03.340 --> 00:19:04.690
Um, could you

00:19:05.020 --> 00:19:06.450
Take me to Chufeng Academy?

00:19:08.260 --> 00:19:08.850
Shanhua.

00:19:17.020 --> 00:19:17.610
Shanhua.

00:19:30.340 --> 00:19:33.450
You really think you can escape?

00:19:48.820 --> 00:19:50.370
Gaolu fell seven years ago.

00:19:51.340 --> 00:19:53.000
Why is Longming Sanctuary still hunting us down?

00:19:53.540 --> 00:19:54.650
Eighteen years ago,

00:19:55.630 --> 00:19:58.170
That traitor stayed in Gaolu's palace for several years

00:19:59.430 --> 00:20:01.000
And then vanished without a trace.

00:20:01.580 --> 00:20:02.170
Tell me!

00:20:02.580 --> 00:20:04.130
Where is that traitor hiding?

00:20:05.500 --> 00:20:07.170
I don't know what you're talking about.

00:20:07.630 --> 00:20:11.040
You'll find out once you get to Longming Sanctuary!

00:20:50.740 --> 00:20:51.480
Xiuyuan!

00:21:32.390 --> 00:21:34.210
- Shanhua. -Are you okay?

00:21:37.020 --> 00:21:37.930
Elder Zhenyun?

00:21:38.820 --> 00:21:41.520
Longming Sanctuary is hunting these Gaolu remnants.

00:21:42.190 --> 00:21:43.930
Is Xingzheng Hall going to interfere?

00:21:45.710 --> 00:21:47.890
You actually got yourselves this beat up by some small fry

00:21:48.020 --> 00:21:49.210
From Longming Sanctuary.

00:21:49.630 --> 00:21:50.410
What do you mean?

00:21:53.020 --> 00:21:54.280
Is Xingzheng Hall

00:21:54.670 --> 00:21:56.370
Really going against Longming Sanctuary?

00:22:26.470 --> 00:22:27.650
His heart meridians are damaged.

00:22:28.100 --> 00:22:30.690
Ordinary medicine won't work anymore.

00:22:35.710 --> 00:22:37.280
Senior, please save Shanhua.

00:22:40.500 --> 00:22:43.320
Gaolu fell seven years ago.

00:22:44.100 --> 00:22:45.560
Why are Longming Sanctuary's people

00:22:45.780 --> 00:22:47.520
Still hunting you?

00:22:52.300 --> 00:22:53.370
I dragged Shanhua into this.

00:22:54.230 --> 00:22:56.850
It's because... I have a spiritual root.

00:22:58.060 --> 00:22:59.480
They won't let me go, fearing I'll become

00:22:59.820 --> 00:23:01.850
A threat later.

00:23:02.910 --> 00:23:04.080
You are incredibly talented.

00:23:05.190 --> 00:23:07.930
You mastered the basic spells Lu Shanhua taught you

00:23:08.190 --> 00:23:10.520
And formed your own style.

00:23:11.740 --> 00:23:12.480
What a pity.

00:23:13.580 --> 00:23:15.450
Xingzheng Hall has made its stance clear.

00:23:15.820 --> 00:23:17.370
We won't interfere in Gaolu's affairs.

00:23:19.540 --> 00:23:20.720
I'm not asking to join Xingzheng Hall.

00:23:21.150 --> 00:23:23.800
I only ask you to save Shanhua.

00:23:25.260 --> 00:23:26.610
Shanhua's life is hanging by a thread.

00:23:27.190 --> 00:23:28.720
To save him,

00:23:29.230 --> 00:23:31.450
We need the power of the nine-tailed fox.

00:23:33.780 --> 00:23:34.930
Nine-tailed fox?

00:23:36.470 --> 00:23:37.320
What a shame.

00:23:43.390 --> 00:23:43.970
Go on.

00:23:48.670 --> 00:23:49.410
Her?

00:23:50.710 --> 00:23:51.890
Find this tomboy

00:23:52.150 --> 00:23:53.970
To track down the nine-tailed fox.

00:23:54.340 --> 00:23:56.210
Remember, do not alert anyone else.

00:23:58.500 --> 00:24:01.080
Especially the immortal sects.

00:24:01.280 --> 00:24:05.080
[Lugong Town]

00:24:07.540 --> 00:24:09.450
Little trinkets! (Watch on www.kisskh.la or www.kisskh.id to support Admin)

00:24:09.470 --> 00:24:11.850
Please take a look. They are for blessings. Really nice.

00:24:12.390 --> 00:24:13.520
Wish you many children and great wealth.

00:24:13.540 --> 00:24:15.370
The ancestral hall in Lugong Town ahead

00:24:15.500 --> 00:24:17.520
Is the registration site for Chufeng Academy.

00:24:17.870 --> 00:24:19.040
I'll only take you this far.

00:24:21.260 --> 00:24:23.080
Mr. Dongyang, you're leaving already?

00:24:24.390 --> 00:24:27.210
Then I won't even have anything to remember you by.

00:24:33.100 --> 00:24:35.130
Here, take this evil-warding bead bracelet.

00:24:40.340 --> 00:24:42.210
Even if you can't get into Chufeng Academy,

00:24:42.670 --> 00:24:44.040
With this bracelet,

00:24:44.710 --> 00:24:46.650
You should be safe.

00:24:51.870 --> 00:24:54.240
Thank you, Mr. Dongyang. You're so kind.

00:24:59.020 --> 00:25:00.480
Then why not help me all the way?

00:25:00.950 --> 00:25:02.280
Any tips

00:25:02.630 --> 00:25:03.800
For getting into Chufeng Academy?

00:25:03.990 --> 00:25:05.080
How can I get in smoothly?

00:25:08.060 --> 00:25:09.170
I wouldn't know.

00:25:09.430 --> 00:25:11.930
Just work hard.

00:25:13.580 --> 00:25:16.370
Then... how do you grow that gourd?

00:25:16.580 --> 00:25:17.280
Can I grow one?

00:25:17.430 --> 00:25:19.210
If I miss you, how do I find you?

00:25:19.820 --> 00:25:21.000
You are so good to me.

00:25:21.020 --> 00:25:22.370
How can I ever repay you?

00:25:29.430 --> 00:25:30.480
Just like Master,

00:25:30.670 --> 00:25:31.890
Always disappearing into thin air.

00:25:34.780 --> 00:25:37.170
Mr. Dongyang, until we meet again!

00:25:42.950 --> 00:25:45.000
I'll find Senior Brother first, then look for Master.

00:25:45.950 --> 00:25:47.930
Chufeng Academy, here I come!

00:25:51.950 --> 00:25:52.720
Make way!

00:26:03.950 --> 00:26:05.370
You again, you menace.

00:26:10.020 --> 00:26:10.720
What do you want?

00:26:13.060 --> 00:26:14.410
I have no money.

00:26:14.820 --> 00:26:16.800
As for looks... I've got even less of that!

00:26:22.870 --> 00:26:23.930
Where did he hide?

00:26:24.340 --> 00:26:26.320
He? Who?

00:26:27.470 --> 00:26:28.410
He...

00:26:29.500 --> 00:26:30.240
He's in...

00:26:30.820 --> 00:26:32.210
He...

00:26:32.390 --> 00:26:33.040
He's in...

00:26:42.820 --> 00:26:44.370
Trying to mug me?

00:26:44.950 --> 00:26:45.800
Come any closer

00:26:45.950 --> 00:26:47.280
And I'll gouge your eyes out!

00:26:57.100 --> 00:26:58.040
Where's my brother?

00:26:58.910 --> 00:27:00.520
Did your assassin accomplices take him?

00:27:00.780 --> 00:27:01.210
Tell me!

00:27:02.190 --> 00:27:03.800
Wait, are you crazy?

00:27:04.150 --> 00:27:05.720
Your brother's missing. Why are you coming after me?

00:27:06.020 --> 00:27:07.170
My master's missing too!

00:27:09.430 --> 00:27:10.720
You menace.

00:27:11.470 --> 00:27:13.170
You showed up out of nowhere in Dongming Town.

00:27:13.870 --> 00:27:14.890
And now you've followed me here.

00:27:15.910 --> 00:27:17.170
Did you harm my master?

00:27:17.390 --> 00:27:18.560
Where did you take him? Tell me!

00:27:20.950 --> 00:27:21.970
You're playing the victim.

00:27:23.230 --> 00:27:25.280
If those assassins aren't your accomplices,

00:27:25.820 --> 00:27:26.930
Then you are Wugou's spy.

00:27:28.340 --> 00:27:30.210
Wugou's spy? What's that?

00:27:46.300 --> 00:27:47.520
I don't have time to waste on you!

00:27:58.910 --> 00:28:00.080
Evil-warding beads?

00:28:08.400 --> 00:28:11.230
♪If legends tell of a perilous land♪

00:28:11.230 --> 00:28:12.690
So many people.

00:28:12.690 --> 00:28:14.120
♪Why not give it a shot and march with all our might?♪

00:28:14.440 --> 00:28:16.880
♪Fearless through a hundred battles, we finally earn our place♪

00:28:17.360 --> 00:28:18.960
♪Happy new semester♪

00:28:18.960 --> 00:28:19.710
[Bu Youran, Chufeng Academy]

00:28:19.710 --> 00:28:20.280
Here you go.

00:28:20.950 --> 00:28:21.610
Thank you.

00:28:21.950 --> 00:28:24.520
♪The fierce gale is grasped tightly in our palms♪

00:28:24.600 --> 00:28:27.280
♪Hearts united, drawing together for a thunderous strike♪

00:28:27.440 --> 00:28:29.520
♪Refusing to coast through life♪

00:28:29.680 --> 00:28:32.160
♪Though a crisis is sealed before us, we will not give up♪

00:28:32.520 --> 00:28:34.780
♪Leaving our silhouettes between heaven and earth♪

00:28:34.780 --> 00:28:35.610
I passed!

00:28:35.630 --> 00:28:36.480
Another one went crazy.

00:28:36.670 --> 00:28:38.850
Yeah. That's the thirty-seventh one today.

00:28:38.870 --> 00:28:39.970
Pass every exam!

00:28:40.150 --> 00:28:41.720
Win every battle!

00:28:41.720 --> 00:28:42.560
♪We will make all the world's pain kneel before us♪

00:28:42.920 --> 00:28:43.780
♪The song of victory never stops♪

00:28:43.780 --> 00:28:46.610
Is this how you usually dress?

00:28:46.610 --> 00:28:47.920
♪The darkness all turns into illusions♪

00:28:48.200 --> 00:28:49.960
♪Unmatched across the Three Realms♪

00:28:50.470 --> 00:28:51.320
Your taste

00:28:52.820 --> 00:28:54.080
Could use some work.

00:28:55.670 --> 00:28:56.280
Name?

00:28:56.670 --> 00:28:57.280
Hometown?

00:28:57.500 --> 00:28:58.760
Which sect are you from?

00:28:59.260 --> 00:29:00.370
My name is Xiaobangchui.

00:29:00.540 --> 00:29:01.240
I'm from Qingqiu.

00:29:01.990 --> 00:29:05.130
Since you are from Qingqiu, do you have a master?

00:29:05.390 --> 00:29:08.040
Have you learned any basic spells?

00:29:08.060 --> 00:29:08.850
I have a master.

00:29:09.470 --> 00:29:11.720
I've learned some talisman drawing.

00:29:12.470 --> 00:29:14.850
Talisman drawing is just a minor trick.

00:29:15.260 --> 00:29:17.000
Nothing impressive.

00:29:41.340 --> 00:29:42.850
[Mr. Li, Elder Zhu, Mr. Cheng, Chufeng Academy] My hometown suffered a flood.

00:29:43.150 --> 00:29:45.890
All my siblings starved to death.

00:29:47.260 --> 00:29:48.720
I stole a bun

00:29:48.870 --> 00:29:50.280
For my severely ill parents.

00:29:51.580 --> 00:29:53.450
But they held my hands tight,

00:29:53.870 --> 00:29:55.650
Refusing to eat the bun till their last breath

00:29:55.740 --> 00:29:56.650
They told me

00:29:56.670 --> 00:29:58.450
I had to try my best to get in here,

00:29:58.950 --> 00:30:01.280
So I'd never suffer from hunger and cold again.

00:30:02.390 --> 00:30:03.040
Only then

00:30:04.340 --> 00:30:08.370
Can they rest in peace.

00:30:14.430 --> 00:30:16.280
Poor child.

00:30:21.020 --> 00:30:22.000
Elder Zhu,

00:30:22.500 --> 00:30:25.450
Should we give her the only special-hardship

00:30:26.390 --> 00:30:27.480
Exam token?

00:30:42.100 --> 00:30:42.760
Hold on.

00:30:47.540 --> 00:30:48.560
[Mu, Chufeng Academy] There is someone here

00:30:48.870 --> 00:30:50.000
Who might be even worse off.

00:31:08.300 --> 00:31:09.760
The fiend.

00:31:10.430 --> 00:31:12.610
Why is this menace here too?

00:31:16.340 --> 00:31:17.170
The dean said

00:31:17.300 --> 00:31:19.610
This selection of disciples is special.

00:31:20.230 --> 00:31:23.130
So he sent me to assist the three of you.

00:31:23.820 --> 00:31:26.280
With you here, we'll have a much easier time.

00:31:26.300 --> 00:31:27.690
Come, have a seat.

00:31:34.340 --> 00:31:35.610
Do you know this young man?

00:31:35.990 --> 00:31:36.800
No.

00:31:38.230 --> 00:31:39.410
I just saw him being chased

00:31:39.870 --> 00:31:41.650
By some Yue State guards outside the town.

00:31:42.150 --> 00:31:43.450
I couldn't stand it,

00:31:43.670 --> 00:31:44.800
So I brought him here.

00:31:46.950 --> 00:31:48.410
I won't interrupt your discussion.

00:31:49.060 --> 00:31:49.610
So I'll just...

00:31:49.820 --> 00:31:50.720
No rush.

00:31:51.230 --> 00:31:52.040
To be fair,

00:31:52.100 --> 00:31:54.000
Let's hear what this young man has to say first.

00:32:02.670 --> 00:32:03.520
My name is Lei Xiuyuan.

00:32:04.470 --> 00:32:06.930
I live in Xigu Village, Luoxia Mountain.

00:32:07.870 --> 00:32:10.560
Xigu Village? You're from Xigu Village?

00:32:14.820 --> 00:32:15.650
Lei Xiuyuan,

00:32:16.150 --> 00:32:18.410
Why do you want to apply to Chufeng Academy?

00:32:34.340 --> 00:32:35.480
These are the names

00:32:36.190 --> 00:32:37.480
Of all 161 people in Xigu Village.

00:32:40.020 --> 00:32:42.130
My family and villagers

00:32:43.470 --> 00:32:45.240
Were slaughtered by evil spirits overnight.

00:32:46.670 --> 00:32:47.610
I have no skills.

00:32:48.100 --> 00:32:50.560
Only by getting into the academy and mastering spells

00:32:51.630 --> 00:32:53.410
Can I have a chance to avenge them.

00:32:54.150 --> 00:32:57.170
He's obviously lying. The masters won't believe him.

00:32:59.470 --> 00:33:01.890
Child, stand up.

00:33:08.950 --> 00:33:11.280
Five years ago, Xigu Village was struck by a demon disaster.

00:33:11.710 --> 00:33:13.970
Several immortal sects sent people to investigate later.

00:33:14.470 --> 00:33:15.800
No survivors were found.

00:33:16.300 --> 00:33:17.130
Then how did you...?

00:33:17.990 --> 00:33:20.890
That night, I was knocked into the river.

00:33:21.580 --> 00:33:22.850
My parents shielded me with their bodies.

00:33:23.470 --> 00:33:24.720
I hid underwater, not daring to make a sound.

00:33:25.260 --> 00:33:26.650
I watched as the whole village was thrown

00:33:26.950 --> 00:33:28.970
Into the river, one by one.

00:33:29.230 --> 00:33:31.080
I am just like those 161 dead people!

00:33:36.060 --> 00:33:37.080
I merely survived.

00:33:37.710 --> 00:33:40.280
Impressive. He acts even better than me.

00:33:40.950 --> 00:33:43.930
Later, I finally found those killers.

00:33:45.540 --> 00:33:46.800
They could use spells.

00:33:48.340 --> 00:33:51.320
They are disciples of Longming Sanctuary from the Wugou State!

00:33:55.580 --> 00:33:57.720
Lei Xiuyuan, do you know

00:33:58.820 --> 00:34:02.210
That mortals get severely punished for slandering immortal sects?

00:34:02.230 --> 00:34:03.130
Every word I said is true.

00:34:03.740 --> 00:34:05.720
This applicant can testify for me.

00:34:12.430 --> 00:34:12.970
Come here.

00:34:16.430 --> 00:34:16.970
Let go.

00:34:17.910 --> 00:34:20.160
That day, I was hiding in a house in Dongming Town

00:34:20.430 --> 00:34:21.600
And ran into Xiaobangchui.

00:34:22.100 --> 00:34:23.480
The assassins were chasing me.

00:34:24.220 --> 00:34:25.890
Thanks to Xiaobangchui's help,

00:34:26.500 --> 00:34:27.480
I managed to escape.

00:34:30.790 --> 00:34:32.890
So, Xiaobangchui,

00:34:33.990 --> 00:34:35.810
Is what he said true?

00:34:39.100 --> 00:34:39.850
Yes, yes.

00:34:40.430 --> 00:34:42.330
Those people were ruthless

00:34:42.350 --> 00:34:43.040
And struck to kill.

00:34:43.350 --> 00:34:44.770
And they all used spells.

00:34:53.140 --> 00:34:54.290
Don't you have a brother?

00:34:54.750 --> 00:34:55.450
Where is he?

00:35:08.220 --> 00:35:09.600
My brother was a disciple of an immortal sect.

00:35:10.700 --> 00:35:11.560
He protected me for years

00:35:12.750 --> 00:35:14.810
But got into trouble and was hunted down.

00:35:15.220 --> 00:35:16.480
Now he's missing.

00:35:26.700 --> 00:35:27.640
The world is vast,

00:35:29.310 --> 00:35:30.480
But there's no place for me

00:35:32.100 --> 00:35:33.200
Unless I get into this academy.

00:35:39.750 --> 00:35:40.850
I don't ask for your pity,

00:35:41.500 --> 00:35:42.600
Only for a chance to take the exam.

00:35:44.540 --> 00:35:46.080
I'd be forever grateful.

00:35:56.990 --> 00:35:57.930
I never expected

00:35:58.310 --> 00:35:59.450
We both have such tragic backgrounds.

00:35:59.750 --> 00:36:01.480
But look, I dress worse

00:36:01.830 --> 00:36:02.640
And live worse than you.

00:36:03.100 --> 00:36:05.200
Plus, I saved your life before.

00:36:06.830 --> 00:36:08.970
I'll always remember your kindness in saving me.

00:36:09.220 --> 00:36:10.640
I'll repay you someday.

00:36:10.830 --> 00:36:12.120
Not "someday". Do it now.

00:36:13.350 --> 00:36:14.680
This is all I have.

00:36:15.140 --> 00:36:16.730
Hope you don't mind.

00:36:18.540 --> 00:36:19.290
If you try to steal my spot again,

00:36:19.310 --> 00:36:20.560
I'll skin you alive!

00:36:20.990 --> 00:36:23.600
I have a blood debt to settle. Please let me have this.

00:36:24.500 --> 00:36:25.450
- I don't want it. - Take it.

00:36:25.470 --> 00:36:26.930
No. Don't force it on me.

00:36:27.660 --> 00:36:28.480
- No. - Here.

00:36:28.790 --> 00:36:30.120
I said no. Let go!

00:36:45.220 --> 00:36:46.250
I didn't even know my parents

00:36:46.270 --> 00:36:47.850
Left me so much money.

00:36:49.990 --> 00:36:50.730
I'm leaving.

00:37:01.990 --> 00:37:03.080
Master,

00:37:03.830 --> 00:37:05.770
It's fine that you abandoned me,

00:37:06.350 --> 00:37:08.290
But at least let things go smoothly for me.

00:37:11.270 --> 00:37:13.520
Now that jinx stole the exam token.

00:37:15.060 --> 00:37:16.480
It cost me so much money to register.

00:37:28.500 --> 00:37:29.680
With that evil-warding beads blocking spiritual detection,

00:37:30.060 --> 00:37:31.200
I'll just capture her first.

00:37:39.100 --> 00:37:40.120
Which loser hit me?

00:37:53.660 --> 00:37:57.680
Prince Ying is arriving! Clear the way!

00:38:03.520 --> 00:38:05.160
[Zhao Mingli, Zhao Zhijie]

00:38:05.680 --> 00:38:06.500
[Lanya]

00:38:06.500 --> 00:38:07.640
Prince Ying is giving out money!

00:38:07.750 --> 00:38:09.250
Prince Ying is giving out money!

00:38:09.500 --> 00:38:10.680
- Let's go! - Prince Ying is giving out money!

00:38:15.870 --> 00:38:17.810
So he's the one throwing money around.

00:38:22.830 --> 00:38:24.200
A rich mark.

00:38:47.060 --> 00:38:48.080
Move! Move!

00:38:48.100 --> 00:38:50.120
Make way, people.

00:38:50.350 --> 00:38:51.000
Get lost!

00:38:52.620 --> 00:38:53.890
Are you okay?

00:38:53.990 --> 00:38:55.200
[Baili Gelin] How can you bully people like that?

00:38:55.750 --> 00:38:56.450
Apologize!

00:38:57.020 --> 00:38:58.640
Prince Ying and Commandery Princess Lanya are here.

00:38:59.020 --> 00:39:00.000
You're nobodies!

00:39:00.270 --> 00:39:00.680
Move!

00:39:00.910 --> 00:39:02.200
I don't care who you are.

00:39:02.580 --> 00:39:03.640
Don't you know how to line up?

00:39:04.500 --> 00:39:05.410
You're the nobody!

00:39:07.310 --> 00:39:08.160
What did you say?

00:39:14.520 --> 00:39:16.280
[Ye Ye]

00:39:19.830 --> 00:39:22.680
I've heard Chufeng Academy treats everyone equally.

00:39:24.830 --> 00:39:27.410
Whether royalty or commoners,

00:39:27.700 --> 00:39:28.600
Everyone is treated the same.

00:39:28.990 --> 00:39:31.120
What do you think, Prince Ying?

00:39:32.910 --> 00:39:34.480
Outrageous! Arrest him!

00:39:36.700 --> 00:39:37.560
Don't be rude!

00:39:41.160 --> 00:39:45.880
[Ji Tongzhou]

00:39:50.540 --> 00:39:51.520
Tongzhou, you're here.

00:39:53.060 --> 00:39:54.480
His Majesty sent you to accompany me for the exam,

00:39:54.870 --> 00:39:56.250
Not to cause trouble.

00:39:56.500 --> 00:39:57.970
I wasn't causing trouble.

00:39:58.430 --> 00:39:59.930
I was afraid you wouldn't get registered,

00:39:59.950 --> 00:40:00.970
So I pushed them aside.

00:40:01.390 --> 00:40:02.040
Besides,

00:40:02.140 --> 00:40:03.370
What's the point of them registering?

00:40:03.700 --> 00:40:04.890
They probably won't get in anyway.

00:40:05.060 --> 00:40:06.250
They're just wasting time.

00:40:06.500 --> 00:40:07.000
You...

00:40:07.390 --> 00:40:09.290
You can't even last one move against my cousin.

00:40:09.310 --> 00:40:11.160
How dare you talk big here?

00:40:12.910 --> 00:40:13.770
Nonsense!

00:40:13.950 --> 00:40:15.680
I just didn't want my whip

00:40:15.700 --> 00:40:16.850
To tear your filthy clothes

00:40:16.870 --> 00:40:17.680
And offend my eyes!

00:40:18.470 --> 00:40:19.520
[Baili Changyue] I heard the Yue State

00:40:19.520 --> 00:40:20.480
Values etiquette above all.

00:40:21.220 --> 00:40:23.290
After seeing how you conduct yourself today,

00:40:24.830 --> 00:40:27.930
It seems the rumors can't be trusted.

00:40:28.180 --> 00:40:28.850
How dare you!

00:40:29.180 --> 00:40:31.120
You lowlife dare to insult our state?

00:40:31.180 --> 00:40:31.890
You're asking for it!

00:40:32.500 --> 00:40:33.290
Forget it.

00:40:33.430 --> 00:40:35.850
Can't win with words so you're ganging up? Bring it on!

00:40:35.870 --> 00:40:36.290
Bring it...

00:40:36.310 --> 00:40:37.000
Yeah, bring it on!

00:40:43.540 --> 00:40:45.930
Move! Get out of the way!

00:40:47.310 --> 00:40:49.680
Seriously, it stinks... back there.

00:40:56.500 --> 00:40:57.480
I'm broke

00:40:57.620 --> 00:40:58.770
After paying the exam fee.

00:40:59.700 --> 00:41:01.600
We'll have to crash here for a few nights.

00:41:04.660 --> 00:41:05.520
It's you guys?

00:41:10.580 --> 00:41:12.680
Thank you for pushing that manure cart.

00:41:12.700 --> 00:41:14.560
That spoiled princess got humiliated.

00:41:15.140 --> 00:41:16.560
By the way, what should we call you?

00:41:17.270 --> 00:41:19.560
I'm Xiaobangchui. And you three are...?

00:41:20.750 --> 00:41:21.520
Xiaobangchui.

00:41:21.700 --> 00:41:23.000
I'm Baili Changyue.

00:41:23.140 --> 00:41:24.600
This is my sister, Baili Gelin.

00:41:26.540 --> 00:41:27.290
I'm Ye Ye.

00:41:27.430 --> 00:41:28.930
I'm Gelin and Changyue's cousin.

00:41:29.540 --> 00:41:31.520
You're cousins?

00:41:53.790 --> 00:41:54.370
Here.

00:42:05.950 --> 00:42:07.040
- Slow down. - It's tasty.

00:42:07.910 --> 00:42:08.930
So delicious.

00:42:08.950 --> 00:42:10.000
It's my cooking, after all.

00:42:10.020 --> 00:42:11.450
Haven't had such a good meal in ages.

00:42:20.180 --> 00:42:20.850
Who's there?

00:42:38.050 --> 00:42:39.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:39.000 --> 00:42:40.550
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:51.800 --> 00:42:55.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

00:42:55.800 --> 00:42:58.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:42:58.560 --> 00:43:01.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

00:43:01.800 --> 00:43:05.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

00:43:05.200 --> 00:43:09.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

00:43:09.360 --> 00:43:12.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

00:43:12.720 --> 00:43:18.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

00:43:19.080 --> 00:43:23.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:43:23.480 --> 00:43:26.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

00:43:26.360 --> 00:43:28.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

00:43:28.400 --> 00:43:32.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:43:32.880 --> 00:43:36.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:43:37.080 --> 00:43:40.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:43:40.160 --> 00:43:46.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

00:43:46.480 --> 00:43:50.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

00:44:03.440 --> 00:44:07.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

00:44:07.400 --> 00:44:10.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:44:10.280 --> 00:44:13.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

00:44:13.680 --> 00:44:17.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

00:44:17.160 --> 00:44:21.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

00:44:21.160 --> 00:44:24.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

00:44:24.600 --> 00:44:30.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

00:44:31.000 --> 00:44:34.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:44:35.200 --> 00:44:37.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

00:44:38.160 --> 00:44:40.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

00:44:40.160 --> 00:44:44.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:44:44.600 --> 00:44:48.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:44:48.720 --> 00:44:51.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:44:51.960 --> 00:44:58.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

00:44:58.720 --> 00:45:02.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

00:45:02.920 --> 00:45:05.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

00:45:05.800 --> 00:45:07.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

00:45:07.880 --> 00:45:12.160
♪Break through the waves, the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

00:45:12.360 --> 00:45:16.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

00:45:16.440 --> 00:45:19.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

00:45:19.600 --> 00:45:25.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

00:45:26.000 --> 00:45:30.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

